%python
import time
import matplotlib as mpl
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.cbook as cbook

def dailyChart(week):
    data = np.loadtxt("topKWithLearning" + str(week), delimiter=',', skiprows=0)
    data2 = np.loadtxt("topKWithoutLearning" + str(week), delimiter=',', skiprows=0)
    day = data[:,0]
    inv = data[:,1]
    nDCG = data[:,2]
    hit = data[:,3]
    day2 = data2[:,0]
    inv2 = data2[:,1]
    nDCG2 = data2[:,2]
    hit2 = data2[:,3]
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(20, 10))
    ax = fig.add_subplot(211)
    ax2 = fig.add_subplot(212)
    
    ax.set_ylabel('nDCG')
    ax2.set_ylabel('hit')
    
    fig.subplots_adjust(right=0.75)
    
    ax2.set_frame_on(True)
    ax2.patch.set_visible(False)
    
    for i in range(0, min(len(day), len(day2))):
        nDCG2[i] = nDCG2[i] * inv2[i] / inv[i]
        hit2[i] = hit2[i] * inv2[i] / inv[i]
    
    ax.plot(day, nDCG, marker='o', color="Red", label="learning")
    ax.plot(day2, nDCG2, marker='o', color="Magenta", label="no learning")
    ax.tick_params(axis='y', colors="Red")
    
    ax2.plot(day, hit, marker='o', color="Blue", label="learning")
    ax2.plot(day2, hit2, marker='o', color="Cyan", label="no learning")
    ax2.tick_params(axis='y', colors="Blue")
    
    ax.set_xlabel('Day (Week '+str(week)+')')
    ax2.set_xlabel('Day (Week '+str(week)+')')
    
    ax.legend()
    ax2.legend()
    ax.grid()
    ax2.grid
    plt.show()

%python
def dailyAggregatedChart(week):
    data = np.loadtxt("topKWithLearning" + str(week), delimiter=',', skiprows=0)
    data2 = np.loadtxt("topKWithoutLearning" + str(week), delimiter=',', skiprows=0)
    day = data[:,0]
    inv = data[:,1]
    nDCG = data[:,2]
    hit = data[:,3]
    day2 = data2[:,0]
    inv2 = data2[:,1]
    nDCG2 = data2[:,2]
    hit2 = data2[:,3]
    
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(20, 10))
    ax = fig.add_subplot(211)
    ax2 = fig.add_subplot(212)
    
    ax.set_ylabel('nDCG')
    ax2.set_ylabel('hit')
    
    fig.subplots_adjust(right=0.75)
    
    ax2.set_frame_on(True)
    ax2.patch.set_visible(False)
    
    for i in range(0, len(day)):
        nDCG[i] = nDCG[:i+1].sum()
        nDCG2[i] = nDCG2[:i+1].sum()
        
        hit[i] = hit[:i+1].sum()
        hit2[i] = hit[:i+1].sum()
        
    vfunc = np.vectorize(lambda x: x / len(day))
    
    nDCG = vfunc(nDCG)
    nDCG2 = vfunc(nDCG2)
    hit = vfunc(hit)
    hit2 = vfunc(hit2)
        
    ax.plot(day, nDCG, marker='o', color="Red", label="learning")
    ax.plot(day2, nDCG2, marker='o', color="Magenta", label="no learning")
    ax.tick_params(axis='y', colors="Red")
    
    ax2.plot(day, hit, marker='o', color="Blue", label="learning")
    ax2.plot(day2, hit2, marker='o', color="Cyan", label="no learning")
    ax2.tick_params(axis='y', colors="Blue")
    
    ax.set_xlabel('Day (Week '+str(week)+')')
    ax2.set_xlabel('Day (Week '+str(week)+')')
    
    ax.legend()
    ax2.legend()
    ax.grid()
    ax2.grid
    plt.show()
